org.forgerock.openam.authentication.service.protocol

Class RemoteHttpServletRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.authentication.service.protocol.RemoteServletRequest
      • org.forgerock.openam.authentication.service.protocol.RemoteHttpServletRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest, javax.servlet.ServletRequest

    public class RemoteHttpServletRequest
extends RemoteServletRequest
implements javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest, Serializable
    This class encapsulates a HttpServletRequest extending from RemoteServletRequest. The information or state that can be serialized is with non serialized content handled sensibly.
    See Also:
